        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Over 80 checks that encourage quality accessibility.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Automatic:</strong>
            checks content on page load.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Customizable:</strong>
            Dozens of props to fine tune the experience for content authors.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Focus on the issues:</strong>
            Turn off irrelevant checks and add exclusions.</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Scalable:</strong>
            Check <em>every</em>
            page for accessibility.</li>
          <li><strong>Shadow DOM support:</strong> Ability to check inside web components or elements with an open Shadow DOM.</li>
        </ul>
